Package: community
Title: Community Analysis Framework
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Biocomplexity Institute", role = c("aut", "cph")),
    person("Micah", "Iserman", role = "cre", email = "micah.iserman@gmail.com")
  )
Imports: cli, data.table, jsonlite, rstudioapi, stats, stringi, Matrix, sf, lingmatch, httpuv
Description: Offers a framework and toolset for the analysis of communities. Helps (1a) assess, clean, and unify
  diverse data sources relating to a community, or (1b) simulate a community, then (2) calculate a range of measures
  of that community, and (3) present and disseminate final data.
URL: https://github.com/uva-bi-sdad/community
BugReports: https://github.com/uva-bi-sdad/community/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
